dd -- delete a line

ndd -- no.of lines delete

yy-- copy a line

nyy -- no.of lines copy

p -- paste

u --undo

dw -- delete a word

ndw - no.of words

x -- char delete (deleting letter by letter)

r -- replace  a letter

R - Continuous replacement

H - Head (cursor moves first line)

G - ground (Cursor goes end line)

$ -- cursor moves to end of the line

^ -- cursor moves to starting of the line

0 -- below the cursor new line

O  -- above the cursor new line

